PolicydWeight - ChangeLog
=========================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Enhancement: Automatically install distribution packages
    Fixed: Delay restart of policyd-weight policy server on i-MSCP upgrade/reconfiguration
    Fixed: Stop and disable policyd-weight policy server on plugin deactivation
    Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.3.x Serie

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: policyd-weight sysvinit script under some distributions doesn't provides status command
    Fixed: Remove space from PolicydWeight service name
    Updated for i-MSCP 1.3.x Serie

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    First release
